vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for and an ordinance granting a Specific Use Permit for a Commercial parking lot or garage use on property zoned Subdistrict 1A within Planned Development District No. 714, the West Commerce Street/Fort Worth Avenue Special Purpose District, on the east line of May Street, south of Harbin Street
Recommendation of Staff and CPC:  Approval for a five-year period, subject to site plan and conditions
Z190-171(CT)
